sources.description: Nora Prentiss is a 1947 American film noir directed by Vincent Sherman and starring Ann Sheridan , Kent Smith , Bruce Bennett , and Robert Alda . It was produced and distributed by Warner Bros. The cinematography is by James Wong Howe and the music was composed by Franz Waxman . The film's sets were designed by the art director Anton Grot .
